reviewText: KELLER AND SCOTT ARE ON THE RUN AFTER A DRUG DEAL GOES BAD.THEY ESCAPED THE COPS AND THE HELICOPTER.THEY FINALLY CAME TO THIS HOUSE.WHILE RELAXING-THEY HEAR A MOAN.SCOTT IS SHOT PRETTY BAD-SO HE DOESN'T INVESTIGATE THE HOUSE,BUT KELLER DOES.THERE'S THIS GUY WRAPPED IN BANDAGES ALL AROUND HIS FACE.HIS FACE IS BLOODY.HE'S IN BED UNDER THE COVERS.THERE'S A NURSE/CARER TAKING CARE OF HIM.AFTER AWHILE,THEY BOTH START TO HEAR THINGS,AND SEE THINGS.THEY FEEL REALLY STRANGE TO BE IN THE HOUSE.IT'S LIKE THEY'RE HALLUCINATING.LATER,KELLER GETS THESE BLOOD DOTS ALL THROUGHOUT HIS BODY.HE'S IN REAL PAIN.BY NOW,THEY BOTH WANT O LEAVE-NOT CARING IF THEY GET CAUGHT AND GO TO PRISON.KELLER HALLUCINATED ONE TIME,AND HE THOUGHT HE SAW THIS WOMAN COMING AFTER HIM TO KILL HIM.HE STABBED HER.HE REALLY STABBED SCOTT-AND KILLED HIM.THIS MOVIE'S ALOT BETTER THAN I'M EXPLAINING.IT'S AN EXCELLENT MOVIE.AND THE ENDING'S EXCELLENT TOO.THE ENDING'S REALLY SOMETHING TO SEE.IT EXPLAINS THE WHOLE MOVIE.THERE'S SUSPENSE,AND EXCITEMENT.IT'S REALLY INTERESTING.IT'S A DIFFERENT HORROR.I HIGHLY RECOMMEND THIS MOVIE!
summary: "NAILED"IS THE PERFECT TITLE FOR THIS MOVIE!
Title: NAILED
